                    From Idea to Automation in Three Steps
                </h2>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                    No coding required. No complex setup. Just describe what you need and let AI do the rest.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
