                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gray-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg">
                            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">1</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                            Describe Your Goal
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
                            Tell us what you want to achieve in plain English. Like "I need to track competitor prices and alert me when they change."
